snippet.title: ARE COVID MANDATES REALLY ENDING? | Fall 2022, Lockdowns and Mandates COME BACK!?
snippet.description:
Meanwhile in BC, Canada, Bonnie Henry (our provincial health officer) has lifted COVID-19 mask and vaccine mandates. BUT... what does this really mean? Are ALL the mandates gone? And are we actually "FREE"? Or is another mutation of covid, a new variant just around the corner going to impend on our rights and freedoms, once again, come this Fall 2022!?

♪MY ORIGINAL SONG "CRAZY" ABOUT COVID, MENTAL HEALTH AND FREEDOM♪👇https://youtu.be/BYDTsTAOEL8
